`M3.S1.C3` A handoff is not a summary.

`M3.S1.C4` A handoff is not a narrative report.

`M3.S1.C5` A handoff is not optional memory.

`M3.S1.C6` A handoff is the binding contract between phases once locked.

`M3.S1.C7` No phase may emit, rename, replace, reinterpret, mutate, or silently repair another phase’s handoff unless the Runtime Spine expressly permits repair through the owner phase or approved repair path.

