`M3.S3.C1` Model emission is not lock.

`M3.S3.C2` A downstream phase may not treat `DRAFT`, `EMITTED`, `REPAIR_REQUESTED`, `FAILED`, or `CONTROLLED_FAILURE` as a locked handoff.

`M3.S3.C3` `LOCKED_WITH_LIMITATIONS` is usable only if limitations remain attached and visible to downstream consumers.

`M3.S3.C4` No phase may erase a prior limitation merely because the next phase can proceed.

