j. Final Output creating new analysis;
k. Renderer rewriting limitations or statuses.

`M5.S7.C3` If a phase needs a fact owned by another phase and the fact is missing, it must not create the missing fact.

`M5.S7.C4` It must request repair, request reinvestigation, use an approved empty state, record limitation, or enter controlled failure.

`M5.S7.C5` Cross-phase contamination blocks handoff lock.

