`M5.S8.C6` Before any phase handoff may lock, the phase must confirm that it did not mutate locked upstream handoffs.

`M5.S8.C7` Before any phase handoff may lock, the phase must confirm that it did not invent facts to satisfy schema.

`M5.S8.C8` Before any phase handoff may lock, the phase must confirm that it did not use rejected, quarantined, inaccessible, private, third-party, unreviewed, or outside-scope material as proof.

