## M6.S1 — Constitutional Function

`M6.S1.C1` This Module defines how The Interface starts a run, routes between phases, validates phase outputs, handles repair, reinvestigation, limitation, and controlled failure, locks final output, and controls rendering.

`M6.S1.C2` Runtime Spine authorizes the route.

`M6.S1.C3` The server/orchestrator executes the route.

