## M6.S10 — Mandatory Disclaimer Rule

`M6.S10.C1` Every final human-facing report or public-facing display must include the mandatory disclaimer.

`M6.S10.C2` The mandatory disclaimer must be carried by `final_output_handoff`.

`M6.S10.C3` Renderer must display the mandatory disclaimer.

`M6.S10.C4` Renderer may style the disclaimer but must not remove, weaken, hide, or materially soften it.

`M6.S10.C5` No final public-facing report may be emitted without the mandatory disclaimer.

Mandatory disclaimer text:

> Public demo. No legal advice. Public or user-provided materials only. Do not submit confidential information. Outputs are demo artifacts requiring qualified legal review before use.

`M6.S10.C6` The disclaimer may be supplemented for clarity, but the substance above must remain intact.

